Alex Lacazette has confirmed he wants to stay at Arsenal. <br />
<br />
The striker has been widely linked with a move away from the Emirates, but fresh from starting and then scoring on the opening day against Fulham, the Frenchman told BT: &quot;I'm really happy. It's only the press who say l am unhappy and l want to leave. But me, from the beginning, I have said I am happy with Arsenal and &quot;I want to play and win titles, we won a title last month, so I am happy with Arsenal.&quot;

